<HEADLINE>
AMERICA'S AMAZING BOOM WILL END. UNTIL THEN, ONE CAN ONLY MARVEL  
 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Commentary, Financial Editors)   (This excellent 700-word ``separate-buy'' article is from the
current (week beginning 5 February 2000) ECONOMIST magazine.)  
  
