<DOC>
<DOCNO> NYT20000206.0189 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-02-06 21:49 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8542 &Cx1f; tab-z
r k BC-WEB-GROCERY-BIZ-ECONO     02-06 0939
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-WEB-GROCERY-BIZ-ECONOMIST-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
